title: Coast to Coast AM - Aug 03 2013 - Researching Prayer
description:
Date:	08-03-13
Host:	John B. Wells
Guests:	Bill Sweet

Hours 1, 2, 3 & 4: John B. Wells was joined by prayer researcher, Bill Sweet, for a discussion on scientific laboratory tests he's conducted to measure the good and bad motivations of prayer and the effectiveness of asking for help from above.
